{"tid":1692431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗添福小食呼籲幫襯同街小食店  食客：要一齊做大黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T12:29:06.000Z","uid":202798,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"deec4705448290fb66bde58fadf536a11d86c620","tid":1692431,"uid":202798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191104/60219971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191104%2F60219971&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=463b592e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191104%2F60219971&h=872b9b92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191104/60219971</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJz2rLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJz2rLe.jpg&h=190d18e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗著名黃店添福小食，早前因公開拒絕做警察生意而爆紅，市民紛紛前來光顧支持，而小店的漢堡和小食即叫即製，令小店大排長龍。位於添福對面街的混醬坊老闆亦有親身排隊支持，在上月29日於Facebook放上巨型炸雞髀的圖，指「終於買到，正嘢」；而添福小食老闆亦隨即轉發，並感謝混醬坊老闆排隊懲罰，更呼籲網民幫忙「報仇」，光顧混醬坊。<br />\n<br />\n網民隨即回應，指兩間黃店老闆惺惺相惜，留言向混醬坊老闆説「下次經過罰埋你」、「我食咗你幾次，都未食到添福」。亦有人呼籲，不要只幫襯著名黃店，要支持其他知名度較低的黃色小店，因為「要實現黃色經濟學很難，手足繼續努力。」<br />\n<br />\n混醬坊主打港式小食如腸粉、魚蛋、鹵水小食、車仔麵及印尼撈麵；招牌$15的鹵水雞髀鹵得入味，肉質嫩滑，店員落單後，會細心地先將雞髀再放入熱騰騰的鹵水浸一段時間；而$16的混醬三寶，則包括燒賣、魚蛋和腸粉。小店由六月開始，已關注反送中運動，一直有在Facebook呼籲市民參與遊行爭取民主，並在遊行日免費派水、響應罷市等。"},{"pid":"381cf56657e01fe2e020a66ac52bd4fe998c3021","tid":1692431,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"上次見到混醬坊唔知藍定黃所以冇買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efeb04b638c50cbb2cf685299dbd07debe0c464","tid":1692431,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"381cf56657e01fe2e020a66ac52bd4fe998c3021","tid":1692431,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"上次見到混醬坊唔知藍定黃所以冇買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"google map認證左係黃"},{"pid":"1f4fa9d04657fdfff08b72cd8584c7311c32a4ea","tid":1692431,"uid":40089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:37:23.000Z","msg":"等陣就去懲罰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d54c6d6dd084ee8d4d30b2822b0fc6614166996","tid":1692431,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:38:12.000Z","msg":"上次去混醬坊無<br />\n真混醬"},{"pid":"0c1ecf985621c49bbc1513a14305841318ee4c2b","tid":1692431,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d54c6d6dd084ee8d4d30b2822b0fc6614166996","tid":1692431,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:38:12.000Z","msg":"上次去混醬坊無<br />\n真混醬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:38:26.000Z","msg":"無開*"},{"pid":"b2327e3d5e850be7c7335777ad1ff6c3cf355cb3","tid":1692431,"uid":37723,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"撚知邊間係黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間間個老闆都十足廢老深藍咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8481a9fc72a25bd72ccc90ea8dfb0b6e6a38d7","tid":1692431,"uid":165200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"「報仇」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d3ba4e7f673694eccd8da63ac9032a59e9e7fe","tid":1692431,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re